+ *
+ * LOCAL PATCH (not upstream — reapply after `npm i -g cyrus-ai`):
+ * Home-relative paths listed in CYRUS_HOME_READ_EXEMPT (colon-separated,
+ * default ".claude/skills") are exempted from the jail so sessions can read
